"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8yyhznfSX_2Z2M7uuwdvg.png?height=720&width=1280)\\n\\n> *Always keep in mind that choosing the right investment option is crucial for making money.*\\n\\nThink about your investment.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/btCTcQ0pxyT_nb9By8oBO.jpg?height=4480&width=6720)\\n\\nCryptocurrencies work as digital assets, and needless to say, more and more people are interested in investing in these currencies.\\n\\nThe value of cryptocurrencies is currently skyrocketing, are you going to seize the opportunity or are you going to let it go?\\n\\n> *If you want to expand your money, you must invest it.*\\n\\nMost wealthy people do it because it allows them to earn much more money by accumulating assets.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8KBFBIOB2ZUgTOv3NnGpM.jpg?height=3425&width=5137)\\n\\nWith cryptocurrencies you will benefit in ways you never imagined.\\n\\nWhen Bitcoin first started trading, no one imagined it would reach $10,000 at some point.\\n\\nHowever, the most significant thing that happened in 2021 was that Bitcoin values crossed $60,000, and Bitcoin received support from several companies and countries.\\n\\nHowever, by mid-May, most cryptocurrencies experienced significant losses.\\n\\nBitcoin values suffered a 17% decline in just 24 hours.\\n\\nChina banned Bitcoin mining and stopped the supply of electricity to Bitcoin miners.\\n\\nInvesting in Bitcoin is a good idea.\\n\\nBitcoin is a rewarding investment, but it also has significant drawbacks.\\n\\nBefore you invest your hard-earned money, pay attention to what I’m telling you.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/z0wr1R6MoNhifd9BOqFMg.jpg?height=3744&width=5616)\\n\\nKeep in mind that bitcoin and cryptocurrencies are a particularly risky investment.\\n\\n> *Never invest more than you can afford to lose; this form of investment can be risky for you.*\\n\\nOnly invest a small portion of your disposable income; this is the right place to start investing with a modest amount.\\n\\nI only tell you this because from my point of view, among all the investment alternatives, I think it is the best alternative.\\n\\nFor example, you could put your money in other cryptocurrencies that are less expensive than Bitcoin.\\n\\n> *Other cryptocurrencies, such as Ethereum, Polkadot, and Cardano, are currently more active and popular.*\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2x8SVWkhi-Zenh5FJfqyM.jpg?height=4469&width=6172)\\n\\nCompared to Bitcoin, these cryptocurrencies have lower prices.\\n\\nHowever, if you are going to invest your money, think twice before doing so.\\n\\nMany times, even if you do it correctly it can be dangerous.\\n\\nIf you are new to cryptocurrencies, the first step is to research the market.\\n\\nIt’s not too difficult.\\n\\nMany investors profit from it, but a large number of investors also lose money.\\n\\n> *To get started, you first need to learn about the bitcoin industry and which cryptocurrencies are currently popular.*\\n\\n> *In addition, you have to make an effort to understand the structure of how cryptocurrencies work and their purpose.*\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/cGzCOnFn96NiVy3qAWSyx.jpg?height=4000&width=6000)\\n\\nBut all this is worth it, because cryptocurrencies are the best long-term investment alternative.\\n\\n## Link to the video:\\n\\n[https://youtu.be/M-Mb365Naak](https://youtu.be/M-Mb365Naak)\\n\\n## Best sites to buy Bitcoin and cryptocurrencies:\\n\\nBinance: \\n <https://bit.ly/3CnGxjx>\\n\\nCoinbase: \\n <https://bit.ly/3zkXl8G>\\n\\nKucoin: \\n <https://bit.ly/3ChMjmt>\\n\\nBitso: \\n <https://bit.ly/3nDI9Bk>\\n\\nStormgain: \\n <https://bit.ly/3EjkHPX>\\n\\n## Social networks:\\n\\n \\n Instagram ModaBitz: \\n <https://bit.ly/3nzSMVY>\\n\\nTwitter: \\n <https://bit.ly/39fBzIS>\\n\\nTik Tok: \\n <https://bit.ly/3hGj6tB>\\n\\nOdysee: \\n <https://bit.ly/3hQcut0>\\n\\nDtube: \\n <https://bit.ly/3kGsMGm>\\n\\nBitTube: \\n <https://bit.ly/3Ck3e8e>\\n\\nRumble: \\n <https://bit.ly/3ESir2l>\\n\\nMedium: \\n <https://bit.ly/3zBRZGk>\\n\\nGab: \\n <https://bit.ly/3Ci9InY>\\n\\nNoise: \\n <https://bit.ly/3lxi5oX>\",\"timestamp\":1633631816,\"title\":\"The time has come to invest in Bitcoin and cryptocurrencies. (Text + Video)\"},\"digest\":\"TFI1-15PR6L0N1YgnaIrqEH6LbZDjiVLSzJV62I5wwU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xF9fE25500D2643A18Eb9f86b8704ADe77D814939\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DezBtEgCWSdYytYoN1v01VCfLiVHnfvmpnbekKAq2ek\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0BYAWyGgDEaIJYK7u2q1w0GVzXVflAafINFgtgmZs2s\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"1qakSdQZtF_r_nwN-sDJhE5cjDPyKQMsE6_yz96sznwDGnzFUjQk2lG7Lf5tR3d9FXp3L1UuyoC3YyJ7o8Rjfw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x5e7ee33d8eab73cec1a1aa4dd8a4448e246fc38db97878ad79747264d7546f8245b3ad066b4f9a7932dbeb0765364a4215128f03fbac9b8d2ca13f98b3e8fba61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DezBtEgCWSdYytYoN1v01VCfLiVHnfvmpnbekKAq2ek\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0BYAWyGgDEaIJYK7u2q1w0GVzXVflAafINFgtgmZs2s\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"TFI1-15PR6L0N1YgnaIrqEH6LbZDjiVLSzJV62I5wwU\"}"